description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the KGHFT Outpatient Service for two Band 2 Health Care Assistants based Kettering OPD. Outpatients are busy, friendly departments and the successful applicant will be required to undertake a range of varied tasks in support of clinical activity. A flexible approach is essential as you may be required to assist in Outpatient departments Trustwide according to service needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants do not need any previous relevant Outpatient experience but a pro-active approach to a rapidly changing service is essential. Personal and professional development is encouraged and supported where applicable to the post. Flexibility regarding hours of duty and location is an essential requirement for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
